object::crbegin

Return a const reverse iterator to the first element of the reversed container.

Synopsis 
const_reverse_iterator
crbegin() const;
Description

The pointed-to element corresponds to the last element of the non-reversed container. If the container is empty, crend() is returned.

Complexity

Constant.

Exception Safety

No-throw guarantee.
